THIRD-PARTY ATTRIBUTION

The coverage shader (slug/frag.kage) is adapted from gpu-font-rendering by
Green Lightning, used under the MIT License:

  Copyright (c) 2022 Green Lightning
  https://github.com/GreenLightning/gpu-font-rendering

  Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy
  of this software and associated documentation files (the "Software"), to deal
  in the Software without restriction [...]. The above copyright notice and this
  permission notice shall be included in all copies or substantial portions of
  the Software.

That work, and this one, build on the winding-number font rendering technique
described by Will Dobbie, Evan Wallace, and Eric Lengyel (Slug). The Slug
algorithm's patent (US #10,373,352) was dedicated to the public domain:

  https://github.com/EricLengyel/Slug
  https://terathon.com/blog/decade-slug.html
